# pytest-aws-fixtures-293984

AWS configuration utilities for Python applications.

## Installation

```bash
pip install pytest-aws-fixtures-293984
```

## Usage

```python
from pytest_aws_fixtures_293984 import get_config, get_client

# Get AWS configuration
config = get_config()

# Get S3 client
s3 = get_client('s3')
```
